## Solutions

### 1. 

, , 

****, 

`num``string`, . `res`.

, 

 **O(n<sup>2</sup>)**,  **O(1)**

```c++
class Solution {
public:
    int maximumSwap(int num) {
        string s = to_string(num), res = s, temp;

        for (int i = 0; i < res.size()-1; i++) {
            for (int j = i+1; j < res.size(); j++) {
                temp = s;
                swap(temp[i], temp[j]);
                res = temp > res ? temp : res;
            }
        }
        return stoi(res);
    }
};
```

